[size=3]Thx to [b]AlgaeEater1[/b] for the Argonian and Khajiit Tail Placement[/size]
[Quote]AlgaeEater1
Hey guys - please read this post if you are having issues with the tail location on Argonians being too low while using CBBE or CHSBHC body type.

First - Visit this mod link here:
[url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2995]http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2995[/url]

Second - Down the optional file named
"Beast Race Beautiful Argonian Tail Mover -universal"


A while back, billystanton worked on a few beast race textures for CBBE when it first came out. He also noticed the tail on Argonians to be way too low, so he made a tail mod that elevated it up to line up with the spine. On the CHSBHC mod, it still is a bit low, but it's much better than without the mod. On CBBE bodies, it should work just fine and makes the tail much higher where it needs to be.

I've uploaded a picture of the tail on my own Argonian in the pictures section to show you how it looks like versus stock. Please make sure to give billystanton credit and kudos if you like his tail mover mod.

I do not know if there is one for Khajiit races though - sorry! If you do find one, let me know.

[color=orange][b]EDIT: [AnTiWoMaAgNoT] : There is Also a Khajiit Tail placement NOW ;)[/b][/color]

[/quote]
